                "context": "Buddhist relic",
                "answer": "The Sacred Tooth Relic is believed to be the left canine tooth of Lord Buddha. "
                          "It has been housed in Sri Lanka since the 4th century CE and is kept in the "
                          "Temple of the Tooth in Kandy. It is the most venerated Buddhist relic in our kingdom.",
                "character": "king"
            },
            {
