            {
                "question": "What were the main exports during Dutch rule?",
                "context": "Trade history",
                "answer": "Cinnamon was our primary export - Ceylon cinnamon being the finest in the world. "
                          "We also traded elephants, pearls, gems, and coconut products. The VOC maintained "
